<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="swift-adj">swift <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /swɪft/    美 /swɪft/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>快的；迅速的；敏捷的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>be <strong>swift to take</strong> measures 
立刻采取措施</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Success was not swift and Rowling might have given up. 
成功并非一蹴而就，罗琳可能也曾放弃过。</p><footer>外研⑥ – 2</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>swiftly /swɪftli/ adv   </p></div>